description: StateHouse Holdings Inc. is involved in the cultivation, processing, manufacture, distribution, and retailing of cannabis products for the adult-use and medical markets in the United States. It operates 13 retail dispensaries in California and one in Oregon; and a retail dispensary in the Haight Ashbury area of San Francisco, California. The company was formerly known as Harborside Inc. and changed its name to StateHouse Holdings Inc. in July 2022. StateHouse Holdings Inc. is headquartered in San Diego, California.
